      <title>Meta 推出新 AI 芯片，旨在减少对 Nvidia 的依赖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/meta-debuts-new-ai-chip-aiming-to-decrease-reliance-on-nvidia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc. 正在部署一款新的国产芯片来帮助其人工智能服务，旨在减少对 Nvidia Corp. 和其他外部公司半导体的依赖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/meta-debuts-new-ai-chip-aiming-to-decrease-reliance-on-nvidia</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
