      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/european-stocks-rebound-with-focus-on-us-inflation-for-rate-cues</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国通胀高于预期，引发人们对利率将在更长时间内保持较高水平的担忧，欧洲股市波动。]]></description>
